Deputy President Mabuza is well 2 August 2020 The Office of the Deputy President has received numerous calls from concerned South Africans regarding the health status of Deputy President David Mabuza. We would like to assure South Africans that the Deputy President is at home and well. Anything contrary to this is a malicious and unfortunate rumour. Statement issued by Matshepo Seedat, Media Liaison Officer inÂ the Office of the Deputy President, 2 August 2020